    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerhouse delivers immediate throttle response with its individual throttle bodies and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise, mechanical throws, transferring power through a reinforced subframe to the M-Variable differential. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, retaining its factory-spec suspension geometry and damping characteristics. Every panel shows original VIN tags with flawless paint depth, and the interior reflects a cabin that has seen minimal UV exposure and zero bolster wear. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
